Kennedy does her monologue on Obama, ISIS, and healthcare.

Tonights panel consists of MICHAEL MALICE, JOE DeVITO, and JULIET HUDDY. First topic of discussion - Obamacare & the supreme court. Yet another investigation reveals TSA to be effectively useless. (73 airport employees have terrorist ties.)

The panel returns to talk about a recent joke made by Clint Eastwood about Caitlyn Jenner. Controversy ensues.

CHARLAMAGNE THA GOD talks about Victor Espinoza being short and still dating hot women. Then they move on to Apple's new streaming music service.

Topical storm:
2,000 piglets lead daring escape from crashed truck in Ohio.
Super sassy 6 year old.
More cat hate from dog lady Kennedy. Adorable dog shields lobster from becoming dinner.
Some guy gets stuck in taco bell drive through, twitters.
Kanye's big 110,000 birthday present. 

The panel returns to talk about Pamela Geller buying billboards representing Muhammad. Email sign-offs. Hope Solo arrest details.

ALEXANDRA ROBBINS stops by to talk about her book "The Nurses". Sex, Drugs, and Nursing.
